    <section id="run" class="grid">
      <div class="card col8">
        <h2>Run locally</h2>
        <ol class="muted" style="margin:10px 0 0 18px">
          <li>Install the .NET SDK (matching the project version).</li>
          <li>Clone the repo.</li>
          <li>Restore + run:</li>
        </ol>
        <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/alvintian/CookAlongAcademy.git
cd CookAlongAcademy
dotnet restore
dotnet run</code></pre>

        <p class="muted" style="margin-top:10px">
          If the project uses a DB locally, you may need to run migrations (only if your project is set up for it):
        </p>
        <pre><code>dotnet ef database update</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="card col4">
